text:
Extremely poor customer experience. Coordination with travel agent was pathetic leading us to wait 3 + hours post check out till they sorted between travel agent Apple Holidays Destination Services @the goldenridge 

Ideally they should have managed this well before our check out time. Staff showed their true colours when spoke to them about this and even raised noise and started shouting quoting hotel policy.  Special mention for this feat for Nilakshya - ops manager for not even asking us to have a seat, offer a coffe except for quoting hotel policy and stating that we cannot leave. Absolutely poor !! Asked to speak to GM - told GM on holiday so cannot disturb him. (Errr - so were we by the way in case the hotel staff missed) 

@appleholidays - your even worse
